{"tid":1933456,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"「心得分享」 教你戰勝股市既心得","createTime":"2020-03-19T09:49:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-20T11:57:57.000Z","uid":123335,"like":36,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"5e565bdb94ece052836ccc14b1563c5da38dc770","tid":1933456,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T09:49:57.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">記住：「市場既事，只能從市場中學」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n1）電視、傳媒果D 財演全部唔洗相信 <br />\n全部都係圖表派，只會叫你穿前頂就追買，穿前底就沽出 <br />\n根本呀婆都識睇，唔洗聽佢地9up 晒時間 <br />\n有留意過佢地d 意見，就會知根本唔準 <br />\ne.g. 前日聽電台，個財演叫個師奶騰訊穿$336 就沽，<br />\n而琴日騰訊真係穿左$336，然後今日又升返去$343 收盤<br />\n如果個師奶沽左就喊到變青姐都似 <br />\n<br />\n2）你係書局搵到既股票書，已經係old news<br />\n果d 咩價值投資，月供etf ，別人恐懼我貪婪 .... etc <br />\n呢d 耳熟能詳既投資心得，只要公開左係Public ，每個人都識既時候 <br />\n就唔會再 work <br />\n你睇下呢排股市撈底死幾多人？<br />\n你睇下班月供etf 、reits、月供正股既，個倉輸左幾多錢？<br />\n「別人恐懼我貪婪 」呢句野害死左幾多人？<br />\nBA 由$330 跌到 $89 ，幾多人俾貪婪害死？<br />\n<br />\n當然，呢D 書作為入門係好好既起步點<br />\n但你一定要建基於呢D old school theory 反覆思考<br />\n透過觀察個市場變化黎驗證你個想法 <br />\nbacktest 唔洗睇得咁重 <br />\n因為股市會一直變化，你30年前岩既，近10年未必會岩 <br />\n10年前岩，今日亦未必岩 <br />\n最重要係你戶口賺緊錢，就代表你岩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\np.s. 我呢排股災賺左好多錢 <br />\n希望大家行少d 冤枉路 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdebbde028ab4b0b96f3b763e07f897782f5b537","tid":1933456,"uid":298077,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T09:51:42.000Z","msg":"温馨提示:<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><em><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">大佬彪</span></ins></em></strong></span>"},{"pid":"9069b8af583f37fe727ee8bd1df50529737e8beb","tid":1933456,"uid":99700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T09:52:12.000Z","msg":"股神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f26551c4bd834edbdc5b034acda8b6005caecb4d","tid":1933456,"uid":67655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T09:53:09.000Z","msg":"我未睇清依家股市個底有幾深<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbd29318253279ac4b021b76eb889b217573eb92","tid":1933456,"uid":133200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T09:53:32.000Z","msg":"點睇向下溝貨定向上溝貨？"},{"pid":"3115349597e2fee29e11be0b9a0dde5e5fdcf67d","tid":1933456,"uid":123335,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T09:53:36.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">記住一句：「市場永遠係正確」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n你鬧個市假，造市<br />\n只係代表你有D 野未睇通 <br />\n錯既，往往係你自己 <br />\n唔好睇得自己咁重 <br />\n你係市場中，連一條鳩毛都稱唔上"},{"pid":"954363bcfdf9202942472edf7d7dc6b9fb00fc4a","tid":1933456,"uid":200529,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T09:56:51.000Z","msg":"想跟大佬彪搵食 夠唔夠班<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JBPad1N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJBPad1N.png&h=160c06fc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"04a0713703002aa8f93d443648cb9192093a7dfb","tid":1933456,"uid":263618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T09:58:06.000Z","msg":"咁究竟睇咩好"},{"pid":"27c075f3ea87e57c0e8f10b161cb4e442276d9d0","tid":1933456,"uid":200529,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T09:58:46.000Z","msg":"好agree最重要係你戶口賺緊錢，就代表你岩<br />\n比人笑tvix賭徒,話知佢"},{"pid":"739ae29b1729f75d01cd038446d8213a8b2d1b3a","tid":1933456,"uid":92512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04a0713703002aa8f93d443648cb9192093a7dfb","tid":1933456,"uid":263618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T09:58:06.000Z","msg":"咁究竟睇咩好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T09:58:55.000Z","msg":"Av"},{"pid":"acd62afe1cb3c024cf8dc73b5884aa963df8b69f","tid":1933456,"uid":164938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T09:59:27.000Z","msg":"平時錢擺銀行唔係好識投資 抱住買股好過擺係銀行心態<br />\n建唔建議而家買2800擺幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/